Let's continue on
this, and let's bring

00:18:40.190 --> 00:18:44.640 align:middle line:84%
in the practical aspect,
too, because sometimes I

00:18:44.640 --> 00:18:48.920 align:middle line:84%
feel that we see it through
just life, and most of us

00:18:48.920 --> 00:18:51.130 align:middle line:84%
walk through just
life as it is, not

00:18:51.130 --> 00:18:54.010 align:middle line:84%
really embracing that thought
that we're a soul, too.

00:18:54.010 --> 00:18:56.200 align:middle line:84%
But do you think
there is a way that it

00:18:56.200 --> 00:18:57.670 align:middle line:90%
can co-exist at all time?

00:18:57.670 --> 00:19:01.300 align:middle line:84%
And is there a solution,
that we can experience spirit

00:19:01.300 --> 00:19:03.280 align:middle line:90%
and physicality all the time?

00:19:03.280 --> 00:19:10.020 align:middle line:84%
And isn't this the key to
having a fulfilled life?

00:19:10.020 --> 00:19:13.900 align:middle line:90%
I think is there all the time.

00:19:13.900 --> 00:19:16.580 align:middle line:84%
Just like the quantum field
is there all the time.

00:19:16.580 --> 00:19:18.280 align:middle line:84%
This is both nothing and
something all the time.

00:19:18.280 --> 00:19:20.020 align:middle line:84%
Spirit is there all the
time, consciousness,

00:19:20.020 --> 00:19:22.520 align:middle line:90%
whatever you call that, being.

00:19:22.520 --> 00:19:24.220 align:middle line:84%
I don't think we can
be conscious of it

00:19:24.220 --> 00:19:26.030 align:middle line:84%
or pay attention
to it all the time.

00:19:26.030 --> 00:19:28.570 align:middle line:90%
Our attention needs to move.

00:19:28.570 --> 00:19:33.290 align:middle line:84%
The art of awakening is that
when you want to, it's there.

00:19:33.290 --> 00:19:35.110 align:middle line:84%
Now at first, it's
hard to do that.

00:19:35.110 --> 00:19:37.500 align:middle line:84%
Because at first it's hard to
do anything with your attention.

00:19:37.500 --> 00:19:40.680 align:middle line:84%
If you want to play the piano,
at first it's hard to do that.

00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:43.280 align:middle line:84%
If you do it a lot, you
can not play for a month,

00:19:43.280 --> 00:19:45.720 align:middle line:84%
and you'll still be able
to sit down and play.

00:19:45.720 --> 00:19:47.710 align:middle line:84%
With this awakening,
it's the same.

00:19:47.710 --> 00:19:50.260 align:middle line:84%
We need to become familiar
with this awake state,

00:19:50.260 --> 00:19:52.974 align:middle line:84%
and then we can pay it
attention, and there it is.

00:19:52.974 --> 00:19:53.940 align:middle line:90%
So it's like a new language.

00:19:53.940 --> 00:19:55.810 align:middle line:10%
Some people say
that playing music

00:19:55.810 --> 00:19:58.240 align:middle line:10%
and playing a new instrument
is learning a new language.

00:19:58.240 --> 00:20:00.380 align:middle line:84%
And we should add
that language-- well,

00:20:00.380 --> 00:20:03.000 align:middle line:84%
some people think that we should
add this language to our world.

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:04.020 align:middle line:90%
So here it's the same.

00:20:04.020 --> 00:20:09.730 align:middle line:10%
We're learning a new mechanism,
a new way of being in life that

00:20:09.730 --> 00:20:12.370 align:middle line:10%
will include all
of those paradox,

00:20:12.370 --> 00:20:14.340 align:middle line:10%
and we can just dwell in that.
Tell us more.

00:20:14.340 --> 00:20:15.040 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:20:15.040 --> 00:20:20.310 align:middle line:84%
I mean, like you said, we live
on the surface most the time.

00:20:20.310 --> 00:20:23.390 align:middle line:90%
We think we know what this is.

00:20:23.390 --> 00:20:25.360 align:middle line:84%
This is why my book's called
"The Mystery Experience,"

00:20:25.360 --> 00:20:28.860 align:middle line:84%
because the key, the
doorway is to realize

00:20:28.860 --> 00:20:30.380 align:middle line:90%
we don't know what this is.

00:20:30.380 --> 00:20:31.870 align:middle line:90%
We have ideas about what it is.

00:20:31.870 --> 00:20:32.780 align:middle line:90%
And we need those.

00:20:32.780 --> 00:20:34.220 align:middle line:90%
That's great.

00:20:34.220 --> 00:20:37.590 align:middle line:84%
But all of our ideas are
like flotsam and jetsam.

00:20:37.590 --> 00:20:41.560 align:middle line:84%
They're like floating around
on this vast ocean of mystery

00:20:41.560 --> 00:20:43.640 align:middle line:90%
that we don't know what this is.

00:20:43.640 --> 00:20:44.510 align:middle line:90%
Nobody does.

00:20:44.510 --> 00:20:46.170 align:middle line:90%
Nobody knows what this is.

00:20:46.170 --> 00:20:48.530 align:middle line:84%
I mean, that's just
phenomenal, just to get that.

00:20:48.530 --> 00:20:50.000 align:middle line:90%
Just sit with that for a minute.

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:50.780 align:middle line:90%
Wow.

00:20:50.780 --> 00:20:54.560 align:middle line:90%
Nobody knows what this is.

00:20:54.560 --> 00:20:58.210 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly you just--
you come out of that,

00:20:58.210 --> 00:21:01.220 align:middle line:90%
and you see the depths of this.

00:21:01.220 --> 00:21:04.990 align:middle line:84%
As you do that, you are able
to see things in new ways.

00:21:04.990 --> 00:21:07.270 align:middle line:90%
So here's another paradoxity.

00:21:07.270 --> 00:21:11.460 align:middle line:84%
I both know and don't
know what this is.

00:21:11.460 --> 00:21:13.620 align:middle line:84%
On the surface, I know
I'm talking with you.

00:21:13.620 --> 00:21:16.400 align:middle line:84%
We're talking about
my philosophy,

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:17.980 align:middle line:84%
we're communicating,
we're sitting

00:21:17.980 --> 00:21:19.490 align:middle line:90%
in a graveyard, da, da, da.

00:21:19.490 --> 00:21:22.070 align:middle line:90%
It's all true.

00:21:22.070 --> 00:21:23.912 align:middle line:90%
But I don't know what life is.

00:21:23.912 --> 00:21:26.660 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what actually
these appearances are.

00:21:26.660 --> 00:21:29.630 align:middle line:84%
I don't know how something can
be both there and not there.

00:21:29.630 --> 00:21:32.590 align:middle line:90%
It's all profoundly mysterious.

00:21:32.590 --> 00:21:35.730 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what, you know,
death and-- [EXHALES]--

00:21:35.730 --> 00:21:39.100 align:middle line:84%
and suddenly, yeah,
I know what it is,

00:21:39.100 --> 00:21:41.550 align:middle line:90%
and I don't know what it is.

00:21:41.550 --> 00:21:45.130 align:middle line:90%
It's all resting on nothing.

00:21:45.130 --> 00:21:47.540 align:middle line:84%
Here's a little thing I
love, a little insight

00:21:47.540 --> 00:21:49.370 align:middle line:90%
which works for me.

00:21:49.370 --> 00:21:53.260 align:middle line:84%
I was just the other day just
thinking, look, everything--

00:21:53.260 --> 00:21:55.300 align:middle line:84%
everything-- this
bench and my body

00:21:55.300 --> 00:21:59.100 align:middle line:84%
and the camera and everything
and the stuff in Australia

00:21:59.100 --> 00:22:03.880 align:middle line:84%
on the other side of the world,
it's all resting on the Earth.

00:22:03.880 --> 00:22:07.596 align:middle line:84%
And the Earth is
resting on nothing.

00:22:07.596 --> 00:22:09.790 align:middle line:90%
[BOTH LAUGHING]

00:22:09.790 --> 00:22:11.430 align:middle line:84%
And that little-- I
mean, it's playful.

00:22:11.430 --> 00:22:12.860 align:middle line:84%
But what it does
to me is that like,

00:22:12.860 --> 00:22:16.010 align:middle line:84%
yeah, that's like
that with my ideas.

00:22:16.010 --> 00:22:18.230 align:middle line:84%
All my ideas seem to
be resting on reality,

00:22:18.230 --> 00:22:20.860 align:middle line:84%
but reality itself is
resting on the mystery.

00:22:20.860 --> 00:22:22.730 align:middle line:90%
You don't know what it is.

00:22:22.730 --> 00:22:24.680 align:middle line:84%
So one of the
doorways in, and why

00:22:24.680 --> 00:22:29.380 align:middle line:84%
I love walking in graveyards,
is because if you come

00:22:29.380 --> 00:22:31.970 align:middle line:84%
into the mystery,
if you recognize,

00:22:31.970 --> 00:22:39.630 align:middle line:84%
oh, this is the wonder
of being that we are,

00:22:39.630 --> 00:22:42.250 align:middle line:84%
suddenly everything
starts to sparkle.

00:22:42.250 --> 00:22:46.980 align:middle line:84%
Suddenly everything is
alive with its magic.

00:22:46.980 --> 00:22:48.140 align:middle line:90%
It's magic now.

00:22:48.140 --> 00:22:50.970 align:middle line:90%
Every moment is magic.

00:22:50.970 --> 00:22:52.890 align:middle line:84%
And for me, the key
thing is that we

00:22:52.890 --> 00:22:56.290 align:middle line:90%
need a philosophy of science.

00:22:56.290 --> 00:23:00.000 align:middle line:10%
You see, the trouble with
reductionism is it kills magic.

00:23:00.000 --> 00:23:02.020 align:middle line:84%
It says, oh, there's no magic.
It's just this.

00:23:02.020 --> 00:23:04.190 align:middle line:90%
Well, that's rubbish. [LAUGHS]

00:23:04.190 --> 00:23:06.860 align:middle line:84%
What science really
says is it's more magic

00:23:06.860 --> 00:23:08.910 align:middle line:90%
than you can possibly imagine.

00:23:08.910 --> 00:23:12.380 align:middle line:84%
It's more incredible than
the mind can comprehend.

00:23:12.380 --> 00:23:16.605 align:middle line:84%
And the more you look at it, the
more you'll just go, wow-- wow.

00:23:16.605 --> 00:23:18.660 align:middle line:90%
And spirituality is the same.

00:23:18.660 --> 00:23:21.550 align:middle line:84%
If you come deep into
the subjective experience

00:23:21.550 --> 00:23:24.000 align:middle line:90%
of your being, wow.

00:23:24.000 --> 00:23:27.754 align:middle line:84%
And then you're awake,
but you're deep awake.

00:23:27.754 --> 00:23:29.620 align:middle line:84%
You're living on the surface,
where it's all doing this,

00:23:29.620 --> 00:23:33.960 align:middle line:84%
and then there's this
deep whoo going on.

00:23:33.960 --> 00:23:36.310 align:middle line:90%
And that changes everything.

00:23:36.310 --> 00:23:38.621 align:middle line:84%
Is there a way that
it could go too deep?

00:23:38.621 --> 00:23:42.230 align:middle line:84%
Too deep?
So deep you start drowning?

00:23:42.230 --> 00:23:45.910 align:middle line:84%
Too deep that we don't live
anymore in reality and make

00:23:45.910 --> 00:23:46.800 align:middle line:90%
things happen.

00:23:46.800 --> 00:23:47.590 align:middle line:90%
Ah, yes.

00:23:47.590 --> 00:23:49.400 align:middle line:84%
Well, you see, there is--
that's a great question,

00:23:49.400 --> 00:23:53.060 align:middle line:84%
because one of the issues I have
that I explore in the book--

00:23:53.060 --> 00:23:54.270 align:middle line:90%
That I keep on writing.

00:23:54.270 --> 00:23:55.472 align:middle line:90%
I'm on my 30th book.

00:23:55.472 --> 00:23:56.710 align:middle line:90%
[BOTH LAUGHING]

00:23:56.710 --> 00:23:57.770 align:middle line:90%
This is the one, though.

00:23:57.770 --> 00:24:01.572 align:middle line:84%
This is the one that I've
pulled it all together-- I hope.

00:24:01.572 --> 00:24:03.840 align:middle line:90%
I take a very playful approach.

00:24:03.840 --> 00:24:06.140 align:middle line:10%
And I have these
discussions with--

00:24:06.140 --> 00:24:07.750 align:middle line:10%
-Thank God for that.
-Yeah.

00:24:07.750 --> 00:24:09.440 align:middle line:84%
We can't take it--
look, life is so

00:24:09.440 --> 00:24:11.350 align:middle line:90%
serious we have to laugh at it.

00:24:11.350 --> 00:24:12.090 align:middle line:90%
Thanks for the Brits.

00:24:12.090 --> 00:24:16.430 align:middle line:84%
--[LAUGHING] Well, humor--
there's a paradoxity.

00:24:16.430 --> 00:24:18.690 align:middle line:84%
Humor works because you take
things that shouldn't sit

00:24:18.690 --> 00:24:20.430 align:middle line:90%
together and put them together.

00:24:20.430 --> 00:24:22.097 align:middle line:84%
That's why humor--
humor's a paradoxity.

00:24:22.097 --> 00:24:23.230 align:middle line:84%
You take something
really serious,

00:24:23.230 --> 00:24:24.770 align:middle line:90%
and you make fun of it.

00:24:24.770 --> 00:24:27.010 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly it's
like, oh, great.

00:24:27.010 --> 00:24:27.910 align:middle line:90%
So we need to do that.

00:24:27.910 --> 00:24:30.290 align:middle line:84%
And what I do, I take something,
which is really precious to me,

00:24:30.290 --> 00:24:31.350 align:middle line:90%
and I make fun of it.

00:24:31.350 --> 00:24:34.180 align:middle line:84%
So I have this character, who
is really a part of me, I guess,

00:24:34.180 --> 00:24:37.810 align:middle line:84%
who I call Swami
Blandananda, and I

00:24:37.810 --> 00:24:39.460 align:middle line:84%
have these little
conversations with Swami

00:24:39.460 --> 00:24:40.970 align:middle line:90%
Blandananda in the book.

00:24:40.970 --> 00:24:44.275 align:middle line:84%
And Swami Blandananda represents
a view of spirituality

00:24:44.275 --> 00:24:49.340 align:middle line:84%
that I have been involved in
myself in the past, which I no

00:24:49.340 --> 00:24:51.000 align:middle line:90%
longer feel comfortable with.

00:24:51.000 --> 00:24:54.550 align:middle line:84%
And what that does is it's
reductionist, like science,

00:24:54.550 --> 00:24:55.860 align:middle line:90%
but in the opposite direction.

00:24:55.860 --> 00:24:57.450 align:middle line:90%
So it rejects life.

00:24:57.450 --> 00:25:00.290 align:middle line:84%
It goes, look, this
is all an illusion.

00:25:00.290 --> 00:25:01.980 align:middle line:10%
It's really all one.

00:25:01.980 --> 00:25:03.920 align:middle line:90%
There is no Tim and Lilou.

00:25:03.920 --> 00:25:05.670 align:middle line:90%
All of this means nothing.

00:25:05.670 --> 00:25:07.350 align:middle line:90%
Just awaken from the dream.

00:25:07.350 --> 00:25:09.730 align:middle line:84%
It's this meaningless thing
that we've got caught up.

00:25:09.730 --> 00:25:14.390 align:middle line:84%
Escape from your bonds, and
you can be in La La Land.

00:25:14.390 --> 00:25:15.220 align:middle line:90%
Well, that's facetious.

00:25:15.220 --> 00:25:17.460 align:middle line:90%
You can be in the great One.

00:25:17.460 --> 00:25:21.680 align:middle line:84%
What that's doing, it seems to
me, is making the same mistake.

00:25:21.680 --> 00:25:23.990 align:middle line:90%
It's still either/or.

00:25:23.990 --> 00:25:28.490 align:middle line:84%
It's going, look, here this
world of separateness is wrong.

00:25:28.490 --> 00:25:29.680 align:middle line:90%
Here it's all one.

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:34.390 align:middle line:84%
As you come back into the deep
self, it truly is all one.

00:25:34.390 --> 00:25:36.600 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, we need to
reject the separateness,

00:25:36.600 --> 00:25:40.010 align:middle line:84%
reject Tim, reject the
ego, reject your humanity,

00:25:40.010 --> 00:25:42.480 align:middle line:84%
reject your emotions,
reject your attachments,

00:25:42.480 --> 00:25:44.800 align:middle line:84%
reject your personal
loves, all the things

00:25:44.800 --> 00:25:48.111 align:middle line:84%
that tie you to separate
and make it seem important.

00:25:48.111 --> 00:25:51.410 align:middle line:84%
Go.
Leave them.

00:25:51.410 --> 00:25:52.880 align:middle line:90%
This is either/or again.

00:25:52.880 --> 00:25:56.670 align:middle line:84%
It's going, it's either
separateness or oneness.

00:25:56.670 --> 00:25:58.260 align:middle line:90%
But it's both.

00:25:58.260 --> 00:25:59.460 align:middle line:90%
It's both.

00:25:59.460 --> 00:26:02.230 align:middle line:84%
It's both one,
and it's separate.

00:26:02.230 --> 00:26:04.810 align:middle line:90%
It's a wave, and it's particles.

00:26:04.810 --> 00:26:05.510 align:middle line:90%
It's not either/or.

00:26:05.510 --> 00:26:07.280 align:middle line:10%
It's both at the same time.

00:26:07.280 --> 00:26:10.000 align:middle line:84%
So what I see is that
reductionist science goes

00:26:10.000 --> 00:26:14.800 align:middle line:84%
out and goes, look, it's
just a mechanical world where

00:26:14.800 --> 00:26:16.250 align:middle line:90%
it's just cause and effect.

00:26:16.250 --> 00:26:19.650 align:middle line:84%
And ultimately what it does
is it divides up reality

00:26:19.650 --> 00:26:21.460 align:middle line:84%
into tiny, tiny,
and tinier, tinier,

00:26:21.460 --> 00:26:26.560 align:middle line:84%
tinier little bits until
you've got little nothing.

00:26:26.560 --> 00:26:29.620 align:middle line:84%
You've explained life
by destroying it.

00:26:29.620 --> 00:26:31.630 align:middle line:84%
And this reductionist
spirituality

00:26:31.630 --> 00:26:33.350 align:middle line:84%
does the same thing in
the other direction.

00:26:33.350 --> 00:26:34.780 align:middle line:84%
It just makes it
bigger and bigger

00:26:34.780 --> 00:26:37.832 align:middle line:84%
into one big oneness until
you've got one big blob.

00:26:37.832 --> 00:26:41.690 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

00:26:41.690 --> 00:26:45.500 align:middle line:84%
In which all of your human
adventure means nothing,

00:26:45.500 --> 00:26:50.260 align:middle line:84%
and you have no freedom,
and none of this is--

00:26:50.260 --> 00:26:53.230 align:middle line:84%
and you've explained
life by destroying it.

00:26:53.230 --> 00:26:58.580 align:middle line:84%
And what we need is a form
of science and spirituality

00:26:58.580 --> 00:27:01.210 align:middle line:84%
which aren't reductionist,
which go, yeah, that is true,

00:27:01.210 --> 00:27:01.980 align:middle line:90%
actually.

00:27:01.980 --> 00:27:04.100 align:middle line:90%
It is all one big wave.

00:27:04.100 --> 00:27:06.490 align:middle line:84%
And we're discrete
little particles.

00:27:06.490 --> 00:27:07.730 align:middle line:84%
So what I'm trying
to articulate is

00:27:07.730 --> 00:27:08.960 align:middle line:90%
a way we can understand that.

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:10.910 align:middle line:84%
So the first step is
paralogical thinking.

00:27:10.910 --> 00:27:13.400 align:middle line:84%
Because then you realize, OK,
so it's going to be opposites.

00:27:13.400 --> 00:27:15.710 align:middle line:84%
It's not going to
be this or that.

00:27:15.710 --> 00:27:17.100 align:middle line:90%
We don't have to choose.

00:27:17.100 --> 00:27:19.880 align:middle line:84%
On a deep level, it's
going to be this and that.

00:27:19.880 --> 00:27:21.510 align:middle line:90%
Both-- and-- not either/or.

00:27:21.510 --> 00:27:23.760 align:middle line:84%
So we're both all one,
and it's all separate.

00:27:23.760 --> 00:27:27.760 align:middle line:84%
Now interestingly, I think
that's what both science

00:27:27.760 --> 00:27:30.130 align:middle line:90%
and deep spirituality say.

00:27:30.130 --> 00:27:32.260 align:middle line:84%
Science is looking
at all the way

00:27:32.260 --> 00:27:35.100 align:middle line:84%
these discrete individual
bits, whether it's

00:27:35.100 --> 00:27:39.080 align:middle line:84%
a body or a cell or an
atom, how do they function?

00:27:39.080 --> 00:27:40.800 align:middle line:84%
And then as it
goes through that,

00:27:40.800 --> 00:27:43.040 align:middle line:84%
it finds this paradoxical
world in which

00:27:43.040 --> 00:27:44.930 align:middle line:90%
it's both waves and particles.

00:27:44.930 --> 00:27:48.570 align:middle line:84%
And below that, there is a
fundamental oneness which

00:27:48.570 --> 00:27:50.980 align:middle line:84%
can't be described,
an energy field,

00:27:50.980 --> 00:27:53.510 align:middle line:84%
something, a mystery
of being from which

00:27:53.510 --> 00:27:54.990 align:middle line:90%
everything is arising.

00:27:54.990 --> 00:27:57.750 align:middle line:84%
But science is
predicated on the idea

00:27:57.750 --> 00:27:59.150 align:middle line:84%
that fundamentally,
everything is one.

00:27:59.150 --> 00:28:02.300 align:middle line:84%
It's all arisen, literally, from
the oneness, the singularity.

00:28:02.300 --> 00:28:05.340 align:middle line:84%
13 and 1/2 billion years ago,
something comes from nothing.

00:28:05.340 --> 00:28:06.890 align:middle line:90%
How paradoxical is that?

00:28:06.890 --> 00:28:10.550 align:middle line:84%
And boomph, it's a
singularity, from one point,

00:28:10.550 --> 00:28:14.330 align:middle line:84%
infinitesimally small
oomph, comes everything.

00:28:14.330 --> 00:28:17.970 align:middle line:84%
So you and I, we
are the singularity.

00:28:17.970 --> 00:28:19.880 align:middle line:90%
Hello, singularity.

00:28:19.880 --> 00:28:20.740 align:middle line:90%
Nice to see you.

00:28:20.740 --> 00:28:24.220 align:middle line:84%
We are the singularity
become conscious of itself

00:28:24.220 --> 00:28:27.600 align:middle line:84%
through this incredible
process of evolution.

