00:29:22.750 --> 00:29:25.600 align:middle line:84%
which could be called God
in traditional language,

00:29:25.600 --> 00:29:27.630 align:middle line:90%
which is like a big mind.

00:29:27.630 --> 00:29:29.920 align:middle line:84%
So here we've looked
outwards, and so we

00:29:29.920 --> 00:29:30.830 align:middle line:90%
see it like an object.

00:29:30.830 --> 00:29:32.650 align:middle line:90%
It's a field of energy.

