Here we look inwards.

00:29:33.680 --> 00:29:35.130 align:middle line:84%
We see the same thing,
but now it looks

00:29:35.130 --> 00:29:37.390 align:middle line:90%
like a subject, not an object.

00:29:37.390 --> 00:29:38.970 align:middle line:90%
It's a great mind.

00:29:38.970 --> 00:29:42.160 align:middle line:84%
It's the one mind,
big mind, in the Zen

00:29:42.160 --> 00:29:47.315 align:middle line:84%
tradition-- God, awareness
in the Hindu tradition.

00:29:47.315 --> 00:29:48.810 align:middle line:90%
The quantum field.

00:29:48.810 --> 00:29:51.720 align:middle line:84%
Quantum field from this
direction, from this direction

00:29:51.720 --> 00:29:58.060 align:middle line:90%
it's a presence.

