is that this is like a dream
arising within one big mind.

00:30:07.920 --> 00:30:08.730 align:middle line:90%
Lucid living.

00:30:08.730 --> 00:30:10.700 align:middle line:84%
That's part of also
what you teach.

00:30:10.700 --> 00:30:12.450 align:middle line:84%
Yes, indeed, although
we'll come back to that.

00:30:12.450 --> 00:30:14.316 align:middle line:84%
We'll come back to that,
because I don't want to clutter

00:30:14.316 --> 00:30:15.300 align:middle line:90%
this idea for a moment.

00:30:15.300 --> 00:30:18.330 align:middle line:84%
So from this perspective,
you've got the field of being,

00:30:18.330 --> 00:30:21.700 align:middle line:84%
which is a mind, dreaming itself
to be everything and everyone.

00:30:21.700 --> 00:30:24.650 align:middle line:84%
And then through the forms that
it's dreaming itself to be,

00:30:24.650 --> 00:30:26.200 align:middle line:90%
it's conscious.

00:30:26.200 --> 00:30:31.370 align:middle line:84%
So the great awareness is
this unconscious being.

00:30:31.370 --> 00:30:33.224 align:middle line:84%
And this is the
dream of Brahman,

00:30:33.224 --> 00:30:34.590 align:middle line:84%
as they would say in
the Hindu tradition.

00:30:34.590 --> 00:30:36.360 align:middle line:90%
It's the dream of God.

00:30:36.360 --> 00:30:39.480 align:middle line:84%
And through dreaming
this, imagining,

00:30:39.480 --> 00:30:42.650 align:middle line:84%
creating this, all these forms,
which aren't really there

00:30:42.650 --> 00:30:47.020 align:middle line:84%
but seem as if they are,
that oneness can now

00:30:47.020 --> 00:30:50.160 align:middle line:90%
take a perspective on itself.

00:30:50.160 --> 00:30:51.724 align:middle line:84%
Now these are the
same thing from two

00:30:51.724 --> 00:30:52.490 align:middle line:90%
different perspectives.

00:30:52.490 --> 00:30:54.350 align:middle line:84%
So what can we say
from both perspectives?

00:30:54.350 --> 00:30:59.250 align:middle line:84%
We can say the one is
become conscious of itself

00:30:59.250 --> 00:31:02.070 align:middle line:84%
through appearing to be
someone, through appearing to be

00:31:02.070 --> 00:31:05.050 align:middle line:84%
individuals, and
that what we are

00:31:05.050 --> 00:31:07.880 align:middle line:84%
are like centers
of consciousness

00:31:07.880 --> 00:31:10.770 align:middle line:90%
within the unconscious field.

00:31:10.770 --> 00:31:12.180 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you look
around you now, you

00:31:12.180 --> 00:31:14.440 align:middle line:84%
will see that the
bench is unconscious,

00:31:14.440 --> 00:31:16.080 align:middle line:90%
the ground is unconscious.

00:31:16.080 --> 00:31:16.880 align:middle line:90%
Most of--

00:31:16.880 --> 00:31:17.770 align:middle line:90%
We don't know.

00:31:17.770 --> 00:31:20.020 align:middle line:84%
Well, not conscious
like we are, let's say.

00:31:20.020 --> 00:31:21.320 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I think
everything is actually

00:31:21.320 --> 00:31:23.540 align:middle line:84%
conscious in its own
way, to be honest.

00:31:23.540 --> 00:31:26.720 align:middle line:84%
But in the traditional way in
terms of looking at itself,

00:31:26.720 --> 00:31:28.910 align:middle line:84%
doing this, the bench isn't
going to pipe up in a minute

00:31:28.910 --> 00:31:30.320 align:middle line:90%
and go, actually I disagree.

00:31:30.320 --> 00:31:31.020 align:middle line:90%
You do?

00:31:31.020 --> 00:31:31.800 align:middle line:90%
You disagree?

00:31:31.800 --> 00:31:33.526 align:middle line:84%
This is an interview
with Tim, Bench.

00:31:33.526 --> 00:31:34.750 align:middle line:84%
What do you mean
I'm not conscious?

00:31:34.750 --> 00:31:35.890 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

00:31:35.890 --> 00:31:37.030 align:middle line:90%
And will you get off me?

00:31:37.030 --> 00:31:40.530 align:middle line:90%
[BOTH LAUGHING]

00:31:40.530 --> 00:31:46.310 align:middle line:84%
Anyway, but in terms
of like raw matter,

00:31:46.310 --> 00:31:49.780 align:middle line:84%
you've got something which is
at least relatively unconscious,

00:31:49.780 --> 00:31:51.830 align:middle line:84%
which has developed
into this complex form,

00:31:51.830 --> 00:31:55.590 align:middle line:90%
which is now conscious.

00:31:55.590 --> 00:31:57.250 align:middle line:84%
That's from the
scientific perspective.

00:31:57.250 --> 00:31:58.460 align:middle line:10%
From the other
perspective, there's

00:31:58.460 --> 00:32:01.210 align:middle line:10%
the field, and the same
thing-- through imagining

00:32:01.210 --> 00:32:04.125 align:middle line:10%
itself to be these forms,
it has become conscious.

00:32:04.125 --> 00:32:08.420 align:middle line:84%
In both ways, we are
centers of consciousness

00:32:08.420 --> 00:32:10.150 align:middle line:90%
in the unconscious field.

00:32:10.150 --> 00:32:16.100 align:middle line:84%
And so the question then
becomes, well, how does this--

00:32:16.100 --> 00:32:17.544 align:middle line:90%
Tunes into that?

00:32:17.544 --> 00:32:19.440 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:32:19.440 --> 00:32:20.250 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:32:20.250 --> 00:32:21.183 align:middle line:90%
You want me to go for that?

00:32:21.183 --> 00:32:22.599 align:middle line:84%
-Yes.
-OK.

00:32:22.599 --> 00:32:23.834 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:32:23.834 --> 00:32:26.370 align:middle line:90%
So here's an image.

00:32:26.370 --> 00:32:30.480 align:middle line:84%
It's just an analogy, shouldn't
be taken too-- pushed too far.

00:32:30.480 --> 00:32:33.350 align:middle line:84%
But I think it
can be insightful.

00:32:33.350 --> 00:32:36.020 align:middle line:84%
For materialists, they have
a whole problem, because they

00:32:36.020 --> 00:32:37.770 align:middle line:90%
go, well, you're a body.

00:32:37.770 --> 00:32:39.820 align:middle line:84%
They ignore the fact
you're not really there.

00:32:39.820 --> 00:32:41.750 align:middle line:84%
You're a body, and
you're conscious,

00:32:41.750 --> 00:32:43.640 align:middle line:84%
and it's something to do with
the piece of complex meat

00:32:43.640 --> 00:32:45.270 align:middle line:90%
in your head.

00:32:45.270 --> 00:32:47.530 align:middle line:84%
The porridge in my head
is somehow conscious.

00:32:47.530 --> 00:32:49.970 align:middle line:90%
And nobody knows how.

00:32:49.970 --> 00:32:52.170 align:middle line:84%
Now clearly, the
brain has something

00:32:52.170 --> 00:32:53.390 align:middle line:90%
to do with consciousness.

00:32:53.390 --> 00:32:55.750 align:middle line:84%
Because if you give me sleeping
pills, I'll fall asleep.

00:32:55.750 --> 00:32:58.147 align:middle line:84%
If you change my chemistry,
I'll fall asleep or hit

00:32:58.147 --> 00:33:01.800 align:middle line:90%
me on the head, and [BABBLES].

00:33:01.800 --> 00:33:04.474 align:middle line:84%
And we've studied the brain
now in great detail and found,

00:33:04.474 --> 00:33:05.640 align:middle line:84%
you know, probe
this, this happens,

00:33:05.640 --> 00:33:07.930 align:middle line:84%
probe this-- so the brain
is obviously something

00:33:07.930 --> 00:33:10.220 align:middle line:90%
to do with consciousness.

00:33:10.220 --> 00:33:12.030 align:middle line:84%
But we can't find
consciousness in it.

00:33:12.030 --> 00:33:14.750 align:middle line:84%
You undo the brain, and you
can't find a single idea.

00:33:14.750 --> 00:33:16.199 align:middle line:84%
Oh, there's an idea.
No.

00:33:16.199 --> 00:33:17.200 align:middle line:90%
All you get is more porridge.

00:33:17.200 --> 00:33:20.070 align:middle line:90%


00:33:20.070 --> 00:33:23.460 align:middle line:84%
What I think this is
pointing to is that what

00:33:23.460 --> 00:33:26.200 align:middle line:84%
spirituality offers to
this is that the awareness

00:33:26.200 --> 00:33:28.440 align:middle line:90%
isn't in the brain.

00:33:28.440 --> 00:33:31.390 align:middle line:90%
The awareness is the field.

00:33:31.390 --> 00:33:34.970 align:middle line:84%
The awareness is the
unconscious field.

00:33:34.970 --> 00:33:39.110 align:middle line:84%
What the brain is doing is
allowing the unconscious field

00:33:39.110 --> 00:33:41.490 align:middle line:90%
to become conscious.

00:33:41.490 --> 00:33:44.170 align:middle line:90%
Here's the analogy.

00:33:44.170 --> 00:33:53.301 align:middle line:84%
Right now, we are in a
field of music, radio waves.

00:33:53.301 --> 00:33:54.800 align:middle line:84%
All these radio-- I
mean, we've got the birds

00:33:54.800 --> 00:33:55.910 align:middle line:90%
singing here, which is nice.

00:33:55.910 --> 00:33:58.930 align:middle line:84%
But we're also-- this air
is full of radio waves.

00:33:58.930 --> 00:34:01.340 align:middle line:84%
There's [HUMMING]
here, [HUMMING]

00:34:01.340 --> 00:34:03.230 align:middle line:84%
classical music over
here, and [HUMMING]--

00:34:03.230 --> 00:34:04.240 align:middle line:90%
all these radio waves.

00:34:04.240 --> 00:34:04.960 align:middle line:90%
And where are they?

00:34:04.960 --> 00:34:06.270 align:middle line:90%
Everywhere.

00:34:06.270 --> 00:34:07.460 align:middle line:90%
We're living in them.

00:34:07.460 --> 00:34:09.500 align:middle line:90%
And it's completely silent.

00:34:09.500 --> 00:34:10.920 align:middle line:90%
Can't hear any of them.

00:34:10.920 --> 00:34:12.030 align:middle line:90%
But they're all there.

00:34:12.030 --> 00:34:13.195 align:middle line:90%
Including electromagnetics.

00:34:13.195 --> 00:34:16.630 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, the lot, all those
fields, all those fields.

00:34:16.630 --> 00:34:19.690 align:middle line:84%
So we're in a field of
music, of radio waves.

00:34:19.690 --> 00:34:21.900 align:middle line:90%
But we can't hear it.

00:34:21.900 --> 00:34:23.469 align:middle line:90%
Take a radio.

00:34:23.469 --> 00:34:29.460 align:middle line:84%
Stick some life in it, some
energy, tune in-- poof--

00:34:29.460 --> 00:34:31.389 align:middle line:84%
and there's this pocket
of sound that will emerge.

00:34:31.389 --> 00:34:33.620 align:middle line:90%
There's music.

00:34:33.620 --> 00:34:36.710 align:middle line:84%
Now, the music's
not in the radio.

00:34:36.710 --> 00:34:39.340 align:middle line:84%
You take the radio to
bits from the transistors,

00:34:39.340 --> 00:34:40.340 align:middle line:90%
where the fuck-- excuse me.

00:34:40.340 --> 00:34:41.800 align:middle line:84%
Where is the--
where's the music?

00:34:41.800 --> 00:34:42.850 align:middle line:90%
Where's the music?

00:34:42.850 --> 00:34:44.480 align:middle line:90%
I can't find the music.

00:34:44.480 --> 00:34:46.550 align:middle line:84%
In fact, this is what
reductionism does.

00:34:46.550 --> 00:34:49.610 align:middle line:84%
It takes the radio to bits, and
there's no music and no radio.

00:34:49.610 --> 00:34:51.770 align:middle line:90%
It's like you've got nothing.

00:34:51.770 --> 00:34:52.560 align:middle line:90%
Where's the music?

00:34:52.560 --> 00:34:53.480 align:middle line:90%
It's not in the radio.

00:34:53.480 --> 00:34:56.010 align:middle line:90%
The music's everywhere.

00:34:56.010 --> 00:34:59.100 align:middle line:84%
The radio is allowing
the music to be heard.

00:34:59.100 --> 00:35:01.346 align:middle line:84%
Well, as an analogy,
I think that can

00:35:01.346 --> 00:35:04.010 align:middle line:84%
point to something about
what's happening right now.

00:35:04.010 --> 00:35:05.640 align:middle line:90%
The awareness is everywhere.

00:35:05.640 --> 00:35:07.270 align:middle line:84%
That's the great
insight of spirituality.

00:35:07.270 --> 00:35:09.580 align:middle line:84%
It's like a giant mind
within which everything

00:35:09.580 --> 00:35:12.110 align:middle line:90%
is arising like a dream.

00:35:12.110 --> 00:35:15.570 align:middle line:84%
What this is doing is allowing
that to become conscious.

00:35:15.570 --> 00:35:18.830 align:middle line:84%
So here's the center
of consciousness,

00:35:18.830 --> 00:35:21.880 align:middle line:84%
a little bubble of consciousness
within the unconscious field.

00:35:21.880 --> 00:35:24.770 align:middle line:84%
And our bubbles of consciousness
have risen together here.

00:35:24.770 --> 00:35:25.800 align:middle line:90%
Hello.

00:35:25.800 --> 00:35:28.700 align:middle line:84%
Now when we part, mine will
disappear off in my direction,

00:35:28.700 --> 00:35:31.870 align:middle line:84%
and yours will disappear
off in your direction,

00:35:31.870 --> 00:35:35.050 align:middle line:84%
and wherever you go,
that center will go.

00:35:35.050 --> 00:35:37.080 align:middle line:84%
And we're centers in
this unconscious field,

00:35:37.080 --> 00:35:38.150 align:middle line:90%
meeting each other.

00:35:38.150 --> 00:35:42.100 align:middle line:90%
But what we are is the field.

00:35:42.100 --> 00:35:45.180 align:middle line:84%
What we are is
everywhere, and always.

00:35:45.180 --> 00:35:48.190 align:middle line:84%
And that is the message
of deep spirituality.

00:35:48.190 --> 00:35:49.820 align:middle line:90%
You are a center.

00:35:49.820 --> 00:35:53.020 align:middle line:84%
But you are also
the whole field.

00:35:53.020 --> 00:35:55.190 align:middle line:84%
You are a center
arising within the field

00:35:55.190 --> 00:35:57.560 align:middle line:84%
and making the
field conscious so

00:35:57.560 --> 00:35:59.720 align:middle line:84%
that you are everywhere
and always if you

00:35:59.720 --> 00:36:01.810 align:middle line:90%
come deep enough into yourself.

00:36:01.810 --> 00:36:03.550 align:middle line:90%
You are the unconscious field.

00:36:03.550 --> 00:36:06.260 align:middle line:84%
Or I am the unconscious
field rising as Tim.

00:36:06.260 --> 00:36:09.820 align:middle line:84%
You are the unconscious
feel arising as Lilou.

00:36:09.820 --> 00:36:12.110 align:middle line:84%
In traditional
language, you'd say,

00:36:12.110 --> 00:36:13.340 align:middle line:90%
you are God arising as Lilou.

00:36:13.340 --> 00:36:15.500 align:middle line:90%
I am God arising as Tim.

00:36:15.500 --> 00:36:20.080 align:middle line:84%
It's just different words
to describe the same thing.

00:36:20.080 --> 00:36:21.620 align:middle line:84%
Normally, we're just
stuck in the center.

00:36:21.620 --> 00:36:23.490 align:middle line:90%
We just think we're this body.

00:36:23.490 --> 00:36:26.920 align:middle line:84%
As you make the journey
to the depths of life,

00:36:26.920 --> 00:36:29.290 align:middle line:90%
you start to discover, oh, no.

00:36:29.290 --> 00:36:30.650 align:middle line:90%
I am the oneness.

00:36:30.650 --> 00:36:33.170 align:middle line:90%
I am the one arising at someone.

00:36:33.170 --> 00:36:36.360 align:middle line:84%
And that's when the deep
awake state kicks in.

00:36:36.360 --> 00:36:41.020 align:middle line:84%
And when it kicks in, life
becomes more wonderful.

00:36:41.020 --> 00:36:42.290 align:middle line:90%
Life becomes wow.

00:36:42.290 --> 00:36:45.820 align:middle line:84%
You just see how incredible
this moment is, every moment is.

00:36:45.820 --> 00:36:50.520 align:middle line:10%
So then it becomes about
remembering that or finding

00:36:50.520 --> 00:36:53.170 align:middle line:10%
little tricks to
remember that we can step

00:36:53.170 --> 00:36:56.110 align:middle line:10%
in the mystery of life anytime
until it becomes a habit

00:36:56.110 --> 00:36:57.650 align:middle line:10%
or something of second nature?

00:36:57.650 --> 00:37:00.290 align:middle line:84%
Because at the beginning as
kids, we need to, of course,

00:37:00.290 --> 00:37:03.770 align:middle line:84%
learn step by step before
we can fully embrace that

00:37:03.770 --> 00:37:05.450 align:middle line:90%
and embody that.

00:37:05.450 --> 00:37:09.120 align:middle line:84%
I'd say make a
habit of wondering.

00:37:09.120 --> 00:37:11.030 align:middle line:84%
I say that because
that's my habit.

00:37:11.030 --> 00:37:12.230 align:middle line:90%
So that's what I know.

00:37:12.230 --> 00:37:14.930 align:middle line:84%
To me, life seems
worthy of wonder.

00:37:14.930 --> 00:37:19.840 align:middle line:84%
If you're not wondering, then
you're already unconscious.

00:37:19.840 --> 00:37:22.060 align:middle line:84%
Because this is
worthy of wonder.

00:37:22.060 --> 00:37:23.980 align:middle line:84%
And if you wonder, you
don't arrive somewhere.

00:37:23.980 --> 00:37:27.800 align:middle line:84%
It's not like, well,
you've got a practice now

00:37:27.800 --> 00:37:29.610 align:middle line:90%
and you can get there.

00:37:29.610 --> 00:37:32.540 align:middle line:84%
What you do is you just open
your journey of life up.

00:37:32.540 --> 00:37:34.580 align:middle line:84%
So your journey, instead
of being just that journey,

00:37:34.580 --> 00:37:36.920 align:middle line:90%
becomes this journey.

00:37:36.920 --> 00:37:39.210 align:middle line:84%
And why it's good
to be in a graveyard

00:37:39.210 --> 00:37:44.040 align:middle line:84%
is because you've got so long
to do this, so why not do it?

00:37:44.040 --> 00:37:47.320 align:middle line:84%
Why not really be alive,
really explore this?

00:37:47.320 --> 00:37:49.710 align:middle line:84%
Why not milk it for
everything it's worth?

00:37:49.710 --> 00:37:53.120 align:middle line:84%
And to do that, if you wonder,
both in the sense of seeing

00:37:53.120 --> 00:37:56.670 align:middle line:84%
how wonderful it is and in
terms of questioning your story,

00:37:56.670 --> 00:38:00.070 align:middle line:84%
looking deeper, finding
more-- who am I really?

00:38:00.070 --> 00:38:01.160 align:middle line:90%
What is this really?

00:38:01.160 --> 00:38:04.180 align:middle line:84%
And as you do that, it
will unfold, undoubtedly.

00:38:04.180 --> 00:38:07.560 align:middle line:84%
You will learn from others, and
you will discover it yourself.

00:38:07.560 --> 00:38:08.310 align:middle line:90%
That's the key.

00:38:08.310 --> 00:38:10.370 align:middle line:90%
And you will.

00:38:10.370 --> 00:38:14.560 align:middle line:84%
If you look deeper, you will
find what you're longing for.

00:38:14.560 --> 00:38:16.810 align:middle line:84%
If you look deeper, you will
find what you're longing for.

00:38:16.810 --> 00:38:20.086 align:middle line:84%
Because what you're
longing for is the depths.

00:38:20.086 --> 00:38:21.600 align:middle line:90%
And let me say why.

00:38:21.600 --> 00:38:24.060 align:middle line:84%
Because I've said used the
words "what you're longing for."

00:38:24.060 --> 00:38:25.760 align:middle line:84%
And there's a very
important word I haven't

00:38:25.760 --> 00:38:27.485 align:middle line:90%
mentioned-- very important.

00:38:27.485 --> 00:38:29.690 align:middle line:84%
And when I hear that,
I hear "purpose" also.

00:38:29.690 --> 00:38:31.620 align:middle line:84%
And I know a lot of people
are looking for their purpose

00:38:31.620 --> 00:38:33.130 align:middle line:84%
and want to contribute
more to life.

00:38:33.130 --> 00:38:35.800 align:middle line:84%
So hopefully this is
related to your answer.

00:38:35.800 --> 00:38:36.730 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:38:36.730 --> 00:38:40.720 align:middle line:84%
Because we have a heart desire
to contribute on this plant.

00:38:40.720 --> 00:38:43.670 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people are realizing
that we're connected

00:38:43.670 --> 00:38:46.160 align:middle line:84%
and that this Earth
needs our help, too.

00:38:46.160 --> 00:38:48.240 align:middle line:90%
And we have a deep longing.

00:38:48.240 --> 00:38:51.900 align:middle line:84%
And we have a deep heart
desire that is waking up,

00:38:51.900 --> 00:38:54.620 align:middle line:84%
as we're waking up
ourselves, to contribute,

00:38:54.620 --> 00:38:57.410 align:middle line:90%
to give, to connect.

00:38:57.410 --> 00:39:00.270 align:middle line:90%


00:39:00.270 --> 00:39:02.700 align:middle line:84%
To me, and then
this is a change

00:39:02.700 --> 00:39:04.780 align:middle line:84%
of tone from where we've
been, but actually it's

00:39:04.780 --> 00:39:06.670 align:middle line:90%
a paralogical complement of it.

00:39:06.670 --> 00:39:10.720 align:middle line:84%
We've been talking in
very conceptual terms

00:39:10.720 --> 00:39:15.920 align:middle line:84%
to say the same thing in
much more emotive language.

00:39:15.920 --> 00:39:17.490 align:middle line:84%
What it seems to
me, from my life

00:39:17.490 --> 00:39:22.910 align:middle line:84%
and from being close to so many
other people, we long for love.

00:39:22.910 --> 00:39:25.420 align:middle line:84%
And that can sound
trite, but it is true.

00:39:25.420 --> 00:39:26.900 align:middle line:90%
We long for love.

00:39:26.900 --> 00:39:32.160 align:middle line:84%
And when we experience
deep love, we love being,

00:39:32.160 --> 00:39:33.190 align:middle line:90%
we love being alive.

00:39:33.190 --> 00:39:35.570 align:middle line:84%
Even when some of it's not
so good, or terrible even,

00:39:35.570 --> 00:39:36.350 align:middle line:90%
we love being.

00:39:36.350 --> 00:39:37.280 align:middle line:90%
We love life.

00:39:37.280 --> 00:39:39.530 align:middle line:90%
And that's what we long to feel.

00:39:39.530 --> 00:39:43.340 align:middle line:84%
And this love arises from
the experience of oneness.

00:39:43.340 --> 00:39:45.100 align:middle line:84%
When you love someone,
it's because you

00:39:45.100 --> 00:39:46.790 align:middle line:90%
don't feel separate from them.

00:39:46.790 --> 00:39:48.180 align:middle line:84%
When you love
nature, it's when you

00:39:48.180 --> 00:39:49.510 align:middle line:90%
don't feel separate from it.

00:39:49.510 --> 00:39:51.530 align:middle line:84%
When you love what you
do, it's because you

00:39:51.530 --> 00:39:52.980 align:middle line:90%
don't feel separate from it.

00:39:52.980 --> 00:39:56.750 align:middle line:84%
When you make the journey
into the deep self,

00:39:56.750 --> 00:39:59.880 align:middle line:84%
you discover this field of
being, which is your essence.

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:01.890 align:middle line:84%
You're not separate
from anything.

00:40:01.890 --> 00:40:06.600 align:middle line:84%
You are separate here and all
one here at the same time.

00:40:06.600 --> 00:40:09.870 align:middle line:84%
And when that oneness and
separateness are there,

00:40:09.870 --> 00:40:11.630 align:middle line:90%
there's this incredible love.

00:40:11.630 --> 00:40:13.380 align:middle line:90%
That's why it's wow.

00:40:13.380 --> 00:40:16.720 align:middle line:84%
Because the love-- it's just
the whole universe is just

00:40:16.720 --> 00:40:21.190 align:middle line:84%
pulsating with love, which
is an emotive way of seeing

00:40:21.190 --> 00:40:22.990 align:middle line:90%
the same thing as oneness.

00:40:22.990 --> 00:40:25.680 align:middle line:90%
Because it's how oneness feels.

00:40:25.680 --> 00:40:28.620 align:middle line:84%
So why this is so important is
because then we find the love.

00:40:28.620 --> 00:40:29.900 align:middle line:90%
Now what is that?

00:40:29.900 --> 00:40:31.270 align:middle line:84%
I mean, how does
that express itself?

00:40:31.270 --> 00:40:35.750 align:middle line:84%
Because love is a
difficult word sometimes.

00:40:35.750 --> 00:40:38.310 align:middle line:90%
Love is a big thing.

00:40:38.310 --> 00:40:42.200 align:middle line:84%
Because love is not just
something I want for me.

00:40:42.200 --> 00:40:44.600 align:middle line:90%
That's not fully love.

00:40:44.600 --> 00:40:46.720 align:middle line:84%
Love is something
which I also give.

00:40:46.720 --> 00:40:48.910 align:middle line:90%
It's something I share.

00:40:48.910 --> 00:40:50.640 align:middle line:84%
And you see another
paradoxity, then,

00:40:50.640 --> 00:40:52.960 align:middle line:84%
which is at the heart
of awakening for me

00:40:52.960 --> 00:40:56.100 align:middle line:84%
and missed by a lot of other
spiritual traditions, I think,

00:40:56.100 --> 00:41:00.350 align:middle line:84%
which is self-realization,
discovering who you are,

00:41:00.350 --> 00:41:05.870 align:middle line:84%
waking up to this and
experiencing that big love.

00:41:05.870 --> 00:41:09.010 align:middle line:84%
And then that love expresses
itself in the world.

00:41:09.010 --> 00:41:12.040 align:middle line:84%
So it's self-realization
and self-expression.

00:41:12.040 --> 00:41:15.290 align:middle line:84%
It's knowing yourself
and then showing in life.

00:41:15.290 --> 00:41:17.020 align:middle line:84%
So you're coming
out, as it were,

00:41:17.020 --> 00:41:20.020 align:middle line:90%
into this wonderful oneness.

00:41:20.020 --> 00:41:22.190 align:middle line:84%
And then there's this
all-embracing love,

00:41:22.190 --> 00:41:26.290 align:middle line:84%
which comes through you out
into the appearances, which

00:41:26.290 --> 00:41:30.360 align:middle line:84%
is service, which
is kindness, which

00:41:30.360 --> 00:41:33.590 align:middle line:84%
is creativity, which
is that longing you

00:41:33.590 --> 00:41:35.100 align:middle line:90%
talk of that we want purpose.

00:41:35.100 --> 00:41:39.240 align:middle line:84%
Well, the deepest purpose
is to learn to love,

00:41:39.240 --> 00:41:41.840 align:middle line:84%
is to learn what it is to love,
which is coming back here,

00:41:41.840 --> 00:41:43.640 align:middle line:84%
and then what it
is to express love,

00:41:43.640 --> 00:41:45.310 align:middle line:90%
which is living your life.

00:41:45.310 --> 00:41:47.540 align:middle line:84%
And if I have
anything as a working

00:41:47.540 --> 00:41:53.080 align:middle line:84%
model for the meaning of my
life, it's learning to love.

00:41:53.080 --> 00:41:55.950 align:middle line:84%
And that embraces for me all of
this philosophy that I've been

00:41:55.950 --> 00:41:57.180 align:middle line:90%
talking about with science.

00:41:57.180 --> 00:42:00.680 align:middle line:84%
That's all the bedrock
of learning to love.

00:42:00.680 --> 00:42:02.930 align:middle line:84%
The journey through
these appearances

00:42:02.930 --> 00:42:06.630 align:middle line:84%
is discovering that
it's one and separate

00:42:06.630 --> 00:42:09.820 align:middle line:84%
and, therefore, feeling
connected and in love

00:42:09.820 --> 00:42:13.610 align:middle line:84%
and then bringing that
deep love into the world

00:42:13.610 --> 00:42:15.220 align:middle line:84%
and making the world
more beautiful,

00:42:15.220 --> 00:42:17.960 align:middle line:84%
more kind, a place
for us to live.

00:42:17.960 --> 00:42:21.320 align:middle line:84%
So if we would learn how to
love and love all that is,

00:42:21.320 --> 00:42:25.640 align:middle line:84%
then eventually our purpose will
just rise out of that instead

00:42:25.640 --> 00:42:29.330 align:middle line:90%
of it being a thinking game?

00:42:29.330 --> 00:42:32.620 align:middle line:84%
I think thinking's good.
[LAUGHING] We need both.

00:42:32.620 --> 00:42:35.000 align:middle line:84%
But sometimes we try to
find our life purpose so much

00:42:35.000 --> 00:42:38.010 align:middle line:84%
and really like it becomes--
I know a lot of people

00:42:38.010 --> 00:42:39.380 align:middle line:84%
are just struggling
with it, and they

00:42:39.380 --> 00:42:42.710 align:middle line:84%
want to-- but it feels to me
and from this conversation,

00:42:42.710 --> 00:42:45.430 align:middle line:84%
too, that if we
focus on the love

00:42:45.430 --> 00:42:48.110 align:middle line:84%
and loving ourselves
and loving every moment,

00:42:48.110 --> 00:42:51.210 align:middle line:84%
there will be something
that will just be even

00:42:51.210 --> 00:42:56.200 align:middle line:84%
more juicy, that will
just be like, ah,

00:42:56.200 --> 00:42:57.860 align:middle line:90%
I really, really love that.

00:42:57.860 --> 00:43:00.030 align:middle line:84%
OK, well, let's approach
this paralogically

00:43:00.030 --> 00:43:01.710 align:middle line:90%
and see if it can help.

00:43:01.710 --> 00:43:04.670 align:middle line:84%
So one of the
paralogical insights

00:43:04.670 --> 00:43:10.090 align:middle line:84%
would be, OK, so maybe what
we need to do is love being

00:43:10.090 --> 00:43:13.560 align:middle line:90%
and then be loving, OK?

00:43:13.560 --> 00:43:15.780 align:middle line:84%
That's what I've been saying, I
think in another language, OK?

00:43:15.780 --> 00:43:17.805 align:middle line:90%
So loving being, being loving.

00:43:17.805 --> 00:43:19.800 align:middle line:90%
We need to those two.

00:43:19.800 --> 00:43:21.775 align:middle line:84%
And then this thing of
purpose-- so maybe purpose

00:43:21.775 --> 00:43:25.260 align:middle line:84%
is paralogical, too, in
which case, one would expect

00:43:25.260 --> 00:43:27.740 align:middle line:84%
that there would be
something universal about it

00:43:27.740 --> 00:43:29.520 align:middle line:84%
and then something
individual about it.

00:43:29.520 --> 00:43:31.620 align:middle line:84%
And when I look at
people and myself,

00:43:31.620 --> 00:43:32.700 align:middle line:90%
that's the way it looks.

00:43:32.700 --> 00:43:34.440 align:middle line:84%
There's a universal
purpose, which

00:43:34.440 --> 00:43:37.240 align:middle line:84%
is true of all of us,
true of life itself,

00:43:37.240 --> 00:43:42.220 align:middle line:84%
which is that life is the one
coming to consciousness as many

00:43:42.220 --> 00:43:44.860 align:middle line:90%
to discover that it's all one.

00:43:44.860 --> 00:43:47.450 align:middle line:84%
Or to put that in emotive
language, it's the one,

00:43:47.450 --> 00:43:50.590 align:middle line:84%
become many, to fall
in love with itself.

00:43:50.590 --> 00:43:52.860 align:middle line:90%
So that applies to all of us.

00:43:52.860 --> 00:43:54.970 align:middle line:84%
We're all on a journey of
becoming more conscious,

00:43:54.970 --> 00:43:57.860 align:middle line:84%
which is also
becoming more loving.

00:43:57.860 --> 00:44:00.590 align:middle line:84%
And then there's the
individual expression.

00:44:00.590 --> 00:44:05.320 align:middle line:84%
That universal love is going to
express through this Tim shape.

00:44:05.320 --> 00:44:07.820 align:middle line:84%
And Tim has these unique
qualities-- and foibles.

00:44:07.820 --> 00:44:09.510 align:middle line:90%
[BOTH LAUGHING]

00:44:09.510 --> 00:44:13.230 align:middle line:84%
He's this unique, paradoxical
bowl of good qualities

00:44:13.230 --> 00:44:15.880 align:middle line:84%
and bad qualities, and he's
a unique thing in the world,

00:44:15.880 --> 00:44:17.030 align:middle line:90%
as everyone is.

00:44:17.030 --> 00:44:19.010 align:middle line:84%
And if the love
pours though Tim,

00:44:19.010 --> 00:44:21.090 align:middle line:84%
it will have a
particular flavor.

00:44:21.090 --> 00:44:24.610 align:middle line:84%
And my flavor is this
philosophy and taking people

00:44:24.610 --> 00:44:26.240 align:middle line:84%
through these
practices that I teach,

00:44:26.240 --> 00:44:28.050 align:middle line:84%
where they can
experience the love.

00:44:28.050 --> 00:44:28.840 align:middle line:90%
That's my job.

00:44:28.840 --> 00:44:30.180 align:middle line:90%
You're a stand-up philosopher.

00:44:30.180 --> 00:44:33.410 align:middle line:84%
Stand-up philosopher,
and really, honest truth,

00:44:33.410 --> 00:44:35.070 align:middle line:90%
a love junkie, really.

00:44:35.070 --> 00:44:36.820 align:middle line:90%
You're a life lover.

00:44:36.820 --> 00:44:39.780 align:middle line:90%
That's for me.

00:44:39.780 --> 00:44:42.180 align:middle line:84%
You can't get enough
[INAUDIBLE], can't you?

00:44:42.180 --> 00:44:45.550 align:middle line:84%
A lovely woman at
one of my retreats

00:44:45.550 --> 00:44:49.204 align:middle line:84%
a while back, when I said,
really I'm a love junkie,

00:44:49.204 --> 00:44:50.770 align:middle line:84%
she went, you're not a
junkie, you're a dealer.

00:44:50.770 --> 00:44:54.450 align:middle line:90%
[BOTH LAUGHING]

00:44:54.450 --> 00:44:55.740 align:middle line:90%
Great job.

00:44:55.740 --> 00:44:57.160 align:middle line:90%
So I'm a love dealer.

00:44:57.160 --> 00:44:58.720 align:middle line:90%
That's really my job.

00:44:58.720 --> 00:45:01.320 align:middle line:84%
But that's because of the
particular life I've lived.

00:45:01.320 --> 00:45:04.300 align:middle line:84%
Now here are you, and
you have had your life,

00:45:04.300 --> 00:45:06.890 align:middle line:84%
and you're discovering the
same oneness and the same love,

00:45:06.890 --> 00:45:08.860 align:middle line:84%
and then it's coming through
this individual form.

00:45:08.860 --> 00:45:10.660 align:middle line:84%
So that's the same
universal purpose.

00:45:10.660 --> 00:45:12.490 align:middle line:84%
And then its
particular expression

00:45:12.490 --> 00:45:14.430 align:middle line:84%
is to be here holding
this microphone,

00:45:14.430 --> 00:45:17.260 align:middle line:84%
being interested in these things
that this mad Englishman has

00:45:17.260 --> 00:45:18.860 align:middle line:90%
got to say.

00:45:18.860 --> 00:45:20.550 align:middle line:90%
And each one of us has that.

00:45:20.550 --> 00:45:27.320 align:middle line:84%
And so when we find the love,
we will find the universal,

00:45:27.320 --> 00:45:29.280 align:middle line:84%
and then we'll find
the particular.

00:45:29.280 --> 00:45:30.490 align:middle line:90%
And it's different for everyone.

00:45:30.490 --> 00:45:32.050 align:middle line:84%
And for some people,
it's can seem

00:45:32.050 --> 00:45:35.300 align:middle line:84%
like it's very big and
grand on a world stage,

00:45:35.300 --> 00:45:39.720 align:middle line:84%
but that's no more significant
than the person who

00:45:39.720 --> 00:45:42.320 align:middle line:90%
is very particular.

00:45:42.320 --> 00:45:45.860 align:middle line:84%
To bring up a child,
what greater-- you know,

00:45:45.860 --> 00:45:49.490 align:middle line:84%
one human being, but to
be so intimately involved

00:45:49.490 --> 00:45:52.450 align:middle line:84%
in bringing another
being into the world

00:45:52.450 --> 00:45:59.530 align:middle line:84%
is as big as being heard by a
million people for 10 minutes.

00:45:59.530 --> 00:46:03.470 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't matter what we do.

00:46:03.470 --> 00:46:09.090 align:middle line:84%
It's that we do what we are
called to with love-- to hold

00:46:09.090 --> 00:46:10.990 align:middle line:84%
the hand of someone
who is dying,

00:46:10.990 --> 00:46:13.780 align:middle line:84%
to be there with our friends,
to be there with ourself,

00:46:13.780 --> 00:46:16.280 align:middle line:84%
to be there caring for
the world-- whatever

00:46:16.280 --> 00:46:18.320 align:middle line:90%
it is that we are drawn to.

00:46:18.320 --> 00:46:20.240 align:middle line:84%
And to see that
if each one of us

00:46:20.240 --> 00:46:22.590 align:middle line:84%
finds that universal
love and then finds

00:46:22.590 --> 00:46:24.640 align:middle line:84%
our universal expression
of it-- sorry,

00:46:24.640 --> 00:46:28.470 align:middle line:84%
individual, particular
expression of it,

00:46:28.470 --> 00:46:32.220 align:middle line:84%
then this will move, because
it's universal and particular.

00:46:32.220 --> 00:46:33.880 align:middle line:90%
That's what we need to do.

00:46:33.880 --> 00:46:35.910 align:middle line:84%
So the more we come
out to the oneness,

00:46:35.910 --> 00:46:38.300 align:middle line:90%
the more we can come into life.

00:46:38.300 --> 00:46:39.610 align:middle line:84%
And the problem
with spirituality

00:46:39.610 --> 00:46:41.260 align:middle line:84%
is that traditionally
it takes you out

00:46:41.260 --> 00:46:43.340 align:middle line:90%
but doesn't bring you back in.

00:46:43.340 --> 00:46:47.490 align:middle line:84%
So you want to find the peace,
but what about the passion?

00:46:47.490 --> 00:46:50.180 align:middle line:84%
You want the stillness,
but what about the action?

00:46:50.180 --> 00:46:52.990 align:middle line:84%
So what we need is one that
goes, yeah, in this moment

00:46:52.990 --> 00:46:56.800 align:middle line:84%
now, there's a deep peace,
and it's arising as passion.

00:46:56.800 --> 00:47:01.480 align:middle line:84%
There's something impersonal,
and it's arising as personal.

00:47:01.480 --> 00:47:03.470 align:middle line:84%
Is that what we called
non-duality, too?

00:47:03.470 --> 00:47:05.740 align:middle line:84%
Non-duality is this,
what I call-- you know,

00:47:05.740 --> 00:47:06.610 align:middle line:90%
it's the oneness.

00:47:06.610 --> 00:47:09.760 align:middle line:10%
It's where there's
no separateness.

00:47:09.760 --> 00:47:10.950 align:middle line:10%
There is no separateness.

00:47:10.950 --> 00:47:12.200 align:middle line:10%
That's the wave.

00:47:12.200 --> 00:47:14.640 align:middle line:10%
But the wave is also a particle.

00:47:14.640 --> 00:47:16.660 align:middle line:84%
And we don't want to ignore
the particle, either.

00:47:16.660 --> 00:47:18.320 align:middle line:84%
We don't want to get
stuck in the separateness.

00:47:18.320 --> 00:47:21.300 align:middle line:84%
If you do, life becomes
small, narrow, and confined.

00:47:21.300 --> 00:47:22.840 align:middle line:10%
Particles are limited.

